---
---

<section id="industrial" class="mx-auto max-w-screen-2xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mb-10">
    <div class="text-ember text-xs tracking-[0.2em] font-semibold mb-2">The Surprising Truth</div>
    <h2 class="section-header tracking-tighter">Heavy machinery &amp; forklifts may transition first.</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-base sm:text-lg text-zinc-400">
      Autonomy is already mature in structured industrial environments where economics and safety align
      perfectly.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
    <article class="tech-surface overflow-hidden">
      <div class="h-44 sm:h-56 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-950 via-zinc-900 to-ink relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-40 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_30%_40%,#f59e0b33,transparent_55%)]"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-5 text-amber-200/80 text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase font-semibold">
          Mining haulage
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
        <div class="uppercase text-xs tracking-widest text-amber-400 mb-2">Mining · Haulage</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl sm:text-2xl tracking-tight mb-3">
          Autonomous Haul Trucks: Already at Scale
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
          <div class="fact pl-4">
            <strong>1,000+</strong> ultra-class autonomous haul trucks by Komatsu (FrontRunner). Over
            <strong>10 billion metric tons</strong> moved autonomously.
          </div>
          <div class="fact pl-4">
            Rio Tinto, Fortescue, Barrick and others run 24/7 autonomous or mixed fleets. Drivers removed
            from hazardous environments.
          </div>
          <div class="fact pl-4">
            Proven benefits: safety, utilization, efficiency. Technology reliable in extreme conditions.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 text-xs inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1.5 rounded-2xl bg-amber-950 text-amber-400">
          Leading L4 autonomy deployment today
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="tech-surface overflow-hidden">
      <div class="h-44 sm:h-56 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-950 via-zinc-900 to-ink relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-40 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_70%_35%,#38bdf833,transparent_55%)]"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-5 text-sky-200/80 text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase font-semibold">
          Warehousing
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 sm:p-8">
        <div class="uppercase text-xs tracking-widest text-sky-400 mb-2">Warehousing &amp; Logistics</div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl sm:text-2xl tracking-tight mb-3">
          Autonomous Forklifts &amp; AMRs: Booming
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
          <div class="fact pl-4">
            Market growing 11–12% CAGR. ABB, Dematic, Jungheinrich, Amazon deploying vision+AI navigation
            in dynamic warehouses.
          </div>
          <div class="fact pl-4">
            Pallet handling, high-rack stacking, dock ops. Solves labor shortages and reduces dangerous
            tasks.
          </div>
          <div class="fact pl-4">
            Structured environments + predictable workflows = clearer ROI and easier autonomy than open
            roads.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-6 text-xs inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1.5 rounded-2xl bg-sky-950 text-sky-400">
          Transforming distribution centers now
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8 bg-ink-soft border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 text-sm">
    <div class="font-medium mb-3">Why industrial leads:</div>
    <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-x-6 gap-y-2 text-xs text-zinc-400">
      <div>· Controlled environments (haul roads, aisles)</div>
      <div>· Massive economic + safety incentive</div>
      <div>· Lower regulatory friction (private property)</div>
      <div>· Repetitive, measurable tasks</div>
      <div>· 24/7 operation without fatigue</div>
      <div>· Immediate, quantifiable ROI</div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-[10px] mt-4 text-zinc-500">
      Public roads are open, adversarial, weather-variable, with fragmented rules and human cultural
      attachment.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
